  n_8fb74677_4c0e_4e02_b997_789b87bfa47f["memory.cpp aims to be SQLite for engineering memory: one local memory layer for developers and AI apps."]
  n_09d945d8_e7d1_44cb_9632_ec39aa068861["Use SQLite as the core store so memory stays local-first, portable, auditable, and easy to back up."]
  n_53c858a6_ff3e_4331_90f3_20937c5b236f["Hybrid retrieval mixes semantic similarity, keyword matching, entity overlap, recency, importance, and confidence."]
  n_ec337dd5_894d_4aba_bfb6_1f3c6238cf46["Expose memory through MCP so Cursor, Claude, Codex, and VS Code can use memory.cpp without custom integrations."]
  n_4995ca54_2b61_4c68_a075_9b1d54269d20["The viral demo is memory proxy plus memory map evolution: every local chat remembers and every repo can explain itself."]
  n_df32996e_1d34_4ab7_9717_3b7215b5d8a3["Bug: the expanded Clap command tree hit a stack-overflow edge case, so v0.2.1 keeps a documented pre-parser with dedicated tests."]
  n_981d198f_5a74_4974_b9ea_3e29bc27d0a6["Fix: split launch-only commands behind a small manual parser, then cover them with smoke tests and parser unit tests."]
  n_436b6db7_b032_4cbd_a45e_4edd264378b6["memory dev morning should summarize yesterday's work, open conflicts, recent decisions, recent bugs, and the next recommended action."]
  n_82609b79_34eb_412d_9a01_8bc0f59ae5a6["memory map evolution should show idea, storage, retrieval, MCP, proxy, attach, and launch polish as a chronological project story."]
  n_480c4857_0e76_452b_9e20_d0d4aabe487c["Attach helpers should default to read-only MCP with workspace scoping and credential redaction so the first integration feels trustworthy."]
  n_2213719b_37c1_4224_964b_24ee4e7ebba7["memory doctor should verify database health, runtime state, map exportability, MCP safety defaults, and Ollama reachability before launch."]
